Name: Old Star Organ Mortar
Description:
Now this is how the Old Star do. With 8 clustered barrels in sets of 4. The Organ Mortar fires volley after volley of homing shells to watever needs to be 6ft under.
                   
 With the help of a very crafty guy, Old Star was able to replicate how GSO created small homing shells. But then the intern said why use the new found homing shell on a small gun. And so the Organ Mortar was created.
